title: Garlic A GoGo- Mediterranean ToGo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Delivery, Take-out, Greek, Turkish, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mobile food truck with vegan choices such as some sauces, dressings, fresh salads, falafel, pita wraps, basmati rice bowls and more. Uses organic when possible. All food is made-in-house. ry/allergy options. Is known for Greek garlic fries which are french fries tossed in a Greek seasoning blend, topped with goat feta and tzatziki; can be made vegan.
